  "description": "\nMonetize Your n8n Workflow with x402\n\nThis workflow lets you monetize any n8n workflow with the x402 payment protocol. \n\nIt uses 1Shot API as the onchain transaction fascilitator role.\n\nCheck out the tutorial video for a complete walkthrough. \n\nSetup\n\nCreate a free 1Shot API account, then go to the API Keys tab and generate a new API key & secret. \nClick on one of the 1Shot API nodes and use the API key & secret from step 1 to create a credentail. You'll need you 1Shot API business ID as well which is located in the top right-hand corner of the 1Shot API dashboard. \nClick on the Payment Token Configs box and enter in the required token information for the x402-compatible tokens you want to accept as payment. Import the x402-compatible tokens you want to accept as payments into your 1Shot API (must be an ERC-20 token with a transferWithAuthorization method) account using the 1Shot Prompts directory. \nClick on the webhook trigger node and set the route. ",
